  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5312529">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5312529/" class="title-link">行文通畅，但缺新意</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5312529"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/6982606/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u6982606-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/6982606/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">骨喷香</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-02-20"
      class="main-meta">2012-02-20 06:23:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5312529_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书写得比较通俗，读起来也很顺。但是看到现在发现很大一部分和第三帝国兴亡史一致。当然此一致绝不仅仅应为所述史实一致，而是遣词行文，多有雷同。鉴于后者早在上世纪六十年代便已成书出版，且世界范围内影响颇大，故本书作者颇有抄袭之嫌。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5312529_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5312529_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










